channel.title: Area Action Compatibility problem
channel.description:
**I am a Chinese player。** **First of all, thank you very much for FICSIT platform and every mod producer。At the same time, I wish you good health。** **My question is, when I uninstall Area Action, will the copied or filled buildings disappear?** **I'm afraid my English is too poor for everyone to understand. I'll say it again in Chinese。**
我是一位中国玩家。 首先，非常感谢Ficsit平台和每一位mod制作者。同时我也祝愿你们身体健康。 我的问题是，当我卸载了Area Action这个mod以后，我所通过Area Action填充或者复制的建筑物会消失吗？
